description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News & ParaShare Bigfoot Hunting Season Edition!

Dave & Tim have their hands full with the weird and wild this week with news from around the world. 

Oklahoma Rep. Justin Humphrey is launching the assault against Sasquatch with his Bigfoot Hunting Season Bill, then we dance our way through The Portal on the Dancefloor, a billionaire is offering $1 million dollars for proof of the afterlife and More!  Plus a brand new Theater of the Mind and the boys read your emailed stories and questions.
